<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<% include ../partials/head %>
	</head>
	<body class="container">
		<header>
			<!-- Trigger the modal with a button -->
			<button type="button" id="info-button" class="btn btn-default btn-circle" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal"><span class="fa fa-question"></span></button>
			<!-- Modal -->
			<div class="modal fade" id="myModal" role="dialog">
				<div class="modal-dialog">
					
					<!-- Modal content-->
					<div class="modal-content">
						<div class="modal-header">
							<button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>
							<h4 class="modal-title">Home Movies</h4>
						</div>
						<div class="modal-body">
							<p>A web app side project created to present the Home Movies collection on Internet Archive in a more focused and interesting way. </p>
							<p>I've always been interested in nostalgia and retro style, so I designed Home Movies as a fun way of evoking this while presenting real home movie videos.</p>
							<br>
							<h5 class="modal-subtitle">Tech Stack</h5>
							<ul class="fa-ul">
								<li><i class="fa-li fa fa-bullseye"></i>Node JS</li>
								<li><i class="fa-li fa fa-bullseye"></i>Express</li>
								<li><i class="fa-li fa fa-bullseye"></i>Redis</li>
								<li><i class="fa-li fa fa-bullseye"></i>Frameworks/Libraries:</li>
								<ul class="fa-ul">
									<li><i class="fa-li fa fa-bullseye"></i>GreenSock's <a href="https://greensock.com/gsap" target="__blank">GSAP</a></li>
									<li><i class="fa-li fa fa-bullseye"></i>SVG Injection <a href="https://github.com/iconic/SVGInjector" target="__blank">library</a></li>
								</ul>
								<li><i class="fa-li fa fa-bullseye"></i>HTML/CSS/Magic</li>
								<li><i class="fa-li fa fa-bullseye"></i>Deployed via Heroku</li>
							</ul>
							<br>
							<h5 class="modal-subtitle">Source Code</h5>
							<p><a href="https://github.com/blunatic/home-movies" target="__blank">GitHub</a></p>
							<h5 class="modal-subtitle">Developer</h5>
							<p><a href="http://brendanluna.com" target="__blank">Brendan Luna</a></p>
						</div>
					</div>
					
				</div>
			</div>
			
		</header>
		<main>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1">
				<h1 class="mainHeading">Home Movies</h1>
				<h2 class="subHeading">Relive the past, one video at a time.</h2>
				<div class="search">
					<img id="loading" class="hidden" src="../images/ajax-loader.gif"/>
					<label id="searchIcon">
						<span class="fa fa-search"></span>
					</label>
					<input id="searchBox" class="form-control" type="text" placeholder="Search...">
					</input>
					<p id="noResults" class="hidden"> No results found! Please try another search.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="row">
			<div id="video" class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1">
				<div class="videoWrapper">
					<img class="tvOff">
					<iframe id="videoFrame" src="" frameborder="0" webkitallowfullscreen="true" mozallowfullscreen="true"allowfullscreen></iframe>
					<button id="hiddenButton1" type="button" class="btn"></button>
					<button id="hiddenButton2" type="button" class="btn"></button>
					<img class="tv-svg inject-me" src="../images/home-movies-tv.svg">
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-12">
				<div id="videoSubtext">
					<h2 id="videoTitle"></h2>
					<h4 id="videoDetails"></h4>
					<h4 id="videoCollection"></h4>
					<p id="videoDescription"></p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<audio id="audio" controls>
    		<source id="fma-song" src="" type="audio/mp3"></source>
		</audio>
		</main>
		<footer>
			<% include ../partials/footer %>
		</footer>
	</body>
</html>